    "description": "属于你的故事、你的自创角、你的七龙珠世界──<br><br>《DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2》是一款动作魄力十足、战斗壮烈，并且具有无限自定义要素的七龙珠游戏。快到游戏内建立自创角探索“肯特都”，并与各个以老师身分登场的角色组队训练，挺身战斗，守护七龙珠的历史吧！<br>随着游戏的发展，将可以自由编辑角色的外表、能力、招式等内容，创造出充满个人特色的强大战士！<br>除此之外，《DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2》内还具有连机游玩模式，可跟世界各地的玩家展开史诗级的战斗，或是参加袭击头目战，一同对抗邪恶的敌人！<br>现在就前往持续更新带来新发现及新体验的肯特都吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >属于你的战士</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/5923f495f1997ea475e919006fecc236.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/5923f495f1997ea475e919006fecc236.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/5923f495f1997ea475e919006fecc236.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>可利用多样的自定义项目，创造出你原创的风格及个性的角色。设定种族、外观、能力甚至是招式，创造出你独一无二的战士吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限的连机体验</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/26e5f52ab0d4485e2a2d4d757c8dff99.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/26e5f52ab0d4485e2a2d4d757c8dff99.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/26e5f52ab0d4485e2a2d4d757c8dff99.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>可在连机游玩模式或游戏内的活动中体验无限战斗的快感！快来跟世界各地的玩家展开史诗级的战斗，或是参加袭击头目战，一同对抗邪恶的敌人吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >燃烧斗志</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/dcc0b2add945eefb3b0d30438ca340b8.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/dcc0b2add945eefb3b0d30438ca340b8.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/dcc0b2add945eefb3b0d30438ca340b8.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>快来参加七龙珠独有的惊心动魄的战斗吧。不管是1对1的战斗，还是与数名敌人展开的大规模战斗，都一定会让你感到热血沸腾！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >七龙珠的世界正在等着你的到来</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/6e2a8cdeed9fa9e85c9e7108eb04ba8f.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/6e2a8cdeed9fa9e85c9e7108eb04ba8f.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/6e2a8cdeed9fa9e85c9e7108eb04ba8f.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>快进入七龙珠的世界！在七龙珠最象征性的场景战斗，与七龙珠系列中具代表性的角色们交流提升实力，并守护七龙珠的历史吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你想要的七龙珠都在这</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/efda69b02085b3e8e70826fd9e1f0f91.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/efda69b02085b3e8e70826fd9e1f0f91.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/efda69b02085b3e8e70826fd9e1f0f91.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2》中，可以体验到系列作中最受粉丝爱戴的标志性角色、场景、故事哦！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >持续延伸</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/ad942c742267eaa76419c904a67c6d36.poster.avif?t=1770607649\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/ad942c742267eaa76419c904a67c6d36.webm?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454650/extras/ad942c742267eaa76419c904a67c6d36.mp4?t=1770607649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2》过往透过发布的付费更新持续新增了《七龙珠Z》、《七龙珠 超》以及剧场版共40名以上的角色、剧情、其他多样的内容！也敬请期待日后的更新！<br><br><strong>※本页显示的画面包含部分游戏本体外可个别购买的内容。</strong>",
